    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "A walk won't fix the fact that I'm just a burden now. Everything is just a slow decline... the doctors, the pills, the doctors visit after doctors visit. It's like I'm just watching my own life disappear bit by bit. It feels so much more dignified than just letting it rot.",
